NUMBER 194
NAME Warehouse
FIXED_LIGHT
DEEPCAVE
*DESCRIPTION_START
Once used by some of Fayd's largest and wealthiest businesses, the warehouse has been abandoned for less remote facilities. Empty boxes and packing crates stacked high against the walls smother you in tranquility, muffling all sound and insulating you from the rush of the outside world. The solitude would be complete if not for a draft circling the room, pushing bits of wadding off shelves that line the southern wall.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT W 195
ITEM 0 282
ITEM 1 378
ITEM 2 420
ITEM 3 341
ITEM 4 877
ITEM 6 349
*DESCRIPTION_START ITEM EXAM 6
It is a big box with a very bright light mounted on it. The light seeks out every corner of the room and illuminates them. There is a switch on it.
*DESCRIPTION_END
ITEM 7 422
IFVERB FLIP 7
  IFVAR ORG = 40
    ECHO PLAYER You activate the security device.
    ECHO OTHERS %N activates the contraption.
    SPELL 406 100
    SPELL 405 100
  ENDIF
  IFVAR ORG ! 40
    ADD FLAG1 1
    IFVAR FLAG1 < 2
      ECHO PLAYER You know you shouldn't mess with things you do not understand.
    ENDIF
    IFVAR FLAG1 >= 2
      ECHO OTHERS %N mishandles the device!
      DAMAGE ELECTRIC 75 %N gets the shock of %h life!
    ENDIF
  ENDIF
ENDIF
IFENTRY
EQUAL TAPPING 0
	IFITEM 5
		ECHO OTHGROUP The shelves swing shut, preventing %n from seeing the passage!
		REMOVEITEM 5
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB KNOCK 0
	IFITEM 5
		ECHO ALL A section of shelves swings shut, concealing a passage!
		EQUAL TAPPING 0
		REMOVEITEM 5
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB KNOCK 0
	ADD TAPPING 1
	IFVAR TAPPING = 3
		ECHO OTHERS As %n knocks the wall for a third time, a section of shelves swings open to reveal a passage!
		ECHO PLAYER As you knock the wall for a third time, a section of shelves swings open to reveal a passage!
		NEWITEM 5 375 ADJ1=282
	ENDIF
ENDIF
IFVERB GO 5
	ECHO PLAYER The shelves swing shut behind you as you step into the secret passage!
	ECHO OTHERS The shelves swing shut as %n steps through the passage.
	REMOVEITEM 5
	EQUAL TAPPING 0
	MOVE 196
	AFFECT 196
	ECHO OTHERS Suddenly a passage opens and %n come through. The passage slams shut behind %i.
	AFFECT 194
	CLEARVERB
ENDIF
