NUMBER 196
NAME Small Room
DARKNESS
INDOOR_FLOOR
*DESCRIPTION_START
Obviously constructed with little attention to flush fittings or clean angles, the tiny room tilts uncomfortably westward toward a row of half-pounded nails. Other than a few scraps of wood and some sawdust, the only object visible here is a panel of buttons set in the wall.
*DESCRIPTION_END
