NUMBER 197
NAME Den
FIXED_LIGHT
DEEPCAVE
*DESCRIPTION_START
Oil lanterns splash this surprisingly large, but cozy, chamber in undulating waves of sultry orange. Dancing to the hypnotic rhythm of flame, the light flits about, playfully highlighting the subtle richness of your surroundings. Fronted by a table of polished ebony, a humongous tooled-leather sofa extends the length of the southern wall. Covered by deeply colored and undoubtedly imported rugs, the floor cushions your feet in an ecstasy of thick pyle. You begin to feel drowsy.
*DESCRIPTION_END
