NUMBER 195
NAME Warehouse
DARKNESS
DEEPCAVE
*DESCRIPTION_START
Crates open, looted and thrown haphazardly into cluttered mounds sharply narrow the building from the east. Pieces of broken boxes and wads of paper packing cover the floor, except for one small space to the west. The area remains clear, roofed by a wide slate slag that hangs precariously over the edge of a wooden bin.
*DESCRIPTION_END
EXIT E 194
EXIT O 279
