NUMBER 650
NAME Night Shades, Guild of Death
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CHANNEL 98
*DESCRIPTION_START
Hewn from resident obsidian that underlies the entire city, the room has been sanded and polished to a satiny black sheen. Red lanterns, set into the ceiling, wash dully over the walls and floor in ever shifting pools of shadow and bloody light. Carved into the eastern and western walls, an archway and a narrow opening lead further into the complex.
*DESCRIPTION_END
