NUMBER 651
NAME Chamber of Light
ASTRAL
FIXED_LIGHT
CHANNEL 98
*DESCRIPTION_START
A gently pulsating glow emanates from deep within the inky stone, casting the chamber in flowing ribbons of brackish red. The very air seems to throb with the cadence of the light, an overwhelming rhythm that courses vein and occupies soul. Other than a dark obelisk looming omnisciently against the western wall, the room is completely bare.
*DESCRIPTION_END
